Contradictory_Signal_Rule: IF active_incident_count > 0 AND attention_required = false → contradictory_signal_count += 1, authority = indeterminate
IF anomaly_adjustments contains high_impact → add 'anomaly_influence' to unverified_signal_refs
IF signal_timestamps are all stale → state = partial, stale_input_count += 1
IF containment_status missing for any incident → state = partial
IF uncontained_count > 0 AND guardrails_holding = true → contradictory_signal_count += 1
